One caution: these tables show the person/proofing lifecycle, but they may not directly show the selected supplier ID. For supplier selection validation, we still need to identify the actual event/result table that stores supplier ID or supplier-specific output. Your AUDIT_PERSON statuses can confirm “SMFA initiated/sent” or “Phone verification initiated,” but to prove 4/5/6 supplier distribution, we still need either RP_EVENT, supplier result tables, or the exact column/table that records KBA_SUPPLIER_ID.
